267
00:24:54,940 --> 00:24:58,200
Naozaj? To je dobré. Gratulujem jej.

268
00:24:59,150 --> 00:25:00,700
To je všetko?

269
00:25:00,700 --> 00:25:02,500
Čo ešte čakáš?

270
00:25:05,620 --> 00:25:07,990
Stále si nahnevaný?

271
00:25:07,990 --> 00:25:09,580
