284
00:25:58,380 --> 00:26:01,780
<i>A ty? Čo pre ňu vieš spraviť ty?</i>

285
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:05,450
<i>Absolútne nič.</i>

286
00:26:19,450 --> 00:26:22,170
