326
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:40,720
Vráť sa do práce.

327
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:42,340
Áno.

328
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:47,700
Ako vidíš,

329
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:50,260
